 2738	 /**
 2739	 * Ensures that the actor has access to all matrix actions from the matrix-actions compendium.
 2740	 * This method will add any missing matrix actions to the actor.
 2741	 *
 2742	 * @returns {Promise<void>}
 2743	 */
