 36	/**
 37	 * The general Shadowrun actor implementation, which currently handles all actor types.
 38	 *
 39	 * To easily access ActorData without any typing issues us the SR6Actor.asCritter helpers.
 40	 * They are set up in a way that will handle both error management and type narrowing.
 41	 * Example:
 42	 * <pre><code>
 43	 * const actor = game.actors.get('randomId');
 44	 * const critter = actor.asCritter();
 45	 * if (!critter) return;
